:: Inventory [nobr]
/%
	Floating-window tab content (auto-registered because this passage
	exists). Replace with your real inventory UI. Any widget macro works
	here, and plain SugarCube markup too.
%/
<<uiCard "Pack">>
	<<uiValue "Gold" $gold "g">>
	<<uiLabel "Your pack is empty.">>
<</uiCard>>

:: Quests [nobr]
/% Floating-window tab content. Replace with your real quest log. %/
<<uiCard "Quests">>
	<<uiCheck "Find out where you are" true>>
	<<uiCheck "Escape this world" false>>
<</uiCard>>
